=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點先叫成熟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你既價值觀符合到佢對你既期望=成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d31c06a91af23620270ecc904cb998a80faca00","tid":217551,"uid":103507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:33:03.000Z","msg":"咁多姊弟戀既呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3497cf189323b624bfb793e76a327eebfea694da","tid":217551,"uid":107539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:39:58.000Z","msg":"年齡真係只係數字，最緊要係大家思想要同歲先係姊弟戀最難做到...<br />\n<br />\n利申:試過同大12年一齊"},{"pid":"3bd5f5395a8f2eb6fc5ea7917ad7e19e097383dc","tid":217551,"uid":103507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年齡真係只係數字，最緊要係大家思想要同歲先係姊弟戀最難做到...<br />\n<br />\n利申:試過同大12年一齊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f00dcb85b3750c40d43dc25cf7686f66ffc77f6","tid":217551,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"介意<br />\nbtw呢度唔絲打<br />\n得假絲<br />\n少量肥絲/毒絲"},{"pid":"28ce11ff6dcf6b830992fb94e4110181119a9123","tid":217551,"uid":107539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>年齡真係只係數字，最緊要係大家思想要同歲先係姊弟戀最難做到...<br />\n<br />\n利申:試過同大12年一齊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當兩個人一齊時其實會有好多心理關口要過<br />\n<br />\n我當年20歲同一個32歲一齊。出街果陣佢唔鍾意拖我手，佢怕會比街上面D人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後一齊左成年先見佢身邊D朋友，其實出到去真係無乜野講，因為大家生活圈同人生階段都唔同，佢D朋友都當你係小朋友咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後係屋企人果關，我阿媽都只係大我女朋友十年，所以不論我阿媽同我女朋友都好難過到自己心理關口，要做好多心理輔導工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657fc158731d1ffcba7382d8e82f757e215b7c27","tid":217551,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>年齡其實冇咩所謂 係睇佢夠唔夠成熟姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把人幾十歲仲on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果大把人都咁諗就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點先叫成熟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼喺段關係度會做返主導嗰個 有事上嚟佢會幫到你面對<br />\n而唔係好似細路咁湊住佢 有事要你呵返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見識過真係難頂到極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25a34478e33eeef9569a333753fcb261cd5ed8f","tid":217551,"uid":59865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>年齡其實冇咩所謂 係睇佢夠唔夠成熟姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把人幾十歲仲on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果大把人都咁諗就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點先叫成熟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼喺段關係度會做返主導嗰個 有事上嚟佢會幫到你面對<br /